<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in New Brighton</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">In the neighbouring McKenzie Town community is a small commercial district, mimicking a typical Main Street one would find in any small town.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">A larger commercial area is located north of McKenzie Towne along 130th avenue.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The street is lined with restaurants, big box stores, pharmacies, and various other retail and miscellaneous shops for people to explore.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located on High Street, the area has a pharmacy, restaurants, cafes, grocery store, and a pub, bringing many needs closer to home.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">New Brighton is located in close proximity to the brand new South Alberta Hospital.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">On High Street and 130th Avenue, there are the doctor and dental clinics to provide easy access for families.</p>
        </div>
